    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_polkinghorne_324500",
        "quote": "After all, the universe required ten billion years of evolution before life was even possible; the evolution of the stars and the evolving of new chemical elements in the nuclear furnaces of the stars were indispensable prerequisites for the generation of life.",
